Cinnamon
base base-devel linux-lts linux-firmware man-db man-pages texinfo vim grub sudo efibootmgr cinnamon gnome-terminal xorg xorg-server dhcpcd dhcp networkmanager os-prober lightdm lightdm-gtk-greeter lightdm-gtk-greeter-settings ttf-roboto noto-fonts [gtk-engine-murrine]
